EN: He spent recklessly and used up all his savings.

ZH: 他的挥霍无度给了他一笔大账单。
EN: His reckless spending led to a hefty bill.

ZH: 她总是挥霍无度，没有理财的概念。
EN: She always spends recklessly without any concept of money management.

ZH: 他挥霍无度的生活方式让他陷入了债务困境。
EN: His extravagant lifestyle has landed him in debt.

