EN: Unrestrained spending can lead to a financial crisis.

ZH: 他挥霍无度的行为让家人为他担忧。
EN: His reckless spending behavior worries his family.

ZH: 让他挥霍无度的原因是缺乏长远规划。
EN: The reason he spends recklessly is the lack of long-term planning.

